description.en:
Dogen Finance is a decentralized autonomous organization with the purpose of bringing Doges into DeFi. Dogen Finance provides a place for all doge-type tokens to generate yield. 

DOGEN token launched on Ethereum at 4:20pm PST on April 20th via yield farming with Uniswap LP tokens for doge-type token pairs. DOGEN farmers earn by combining their DOGE-related tokens such as renDOGE, SHIB, and AKITA with ETH in Uniswap and staking the resulting pool token in a Dogen Finance dog park on the ""Parks"" page. 

Dogen Finance is community-governed and works together to crowdsourced yield generation strategies. Based on the model of BadgerDAO, whose purpose is bringing Bitcoin to DeFi, Dogen Finance brings Doges to DeFi.
